OL,3,CStarmer vows to 'get the balance
OL,4,Cright' after Hillsborough Law
OL,5,Camendment pulled
OL,7,FThe legislation was scheduled to be
OL,8,Fdebated by Parliament on Monday 19
OL,9,FJanuary, but it was withdrawn entirely
OL,10,Fon Sunday.
OL,12,FKnown as the Hillsborough Law, the
OL,13,FBill is intended to make sure the
OL,14,Fauthorities will face criminal
OL,15,Fsanctions if they attempt to cover up
OL,16,Fthe facts behind disasters such as the
OL,17,F1989 Hillsborough tragedy or the 2017
OL,18,FGrenfell Tower fire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
