OL,3,CStarmer vows to 'get the balance
OL,4,Cright' after Hillsborough Law
OL,5,Camendment pulled
OL,7,FConcerns were raised that intelligence
OL,8,Fagencies could have used the amendment
OL,9,Fto avoid being bound by the proposed
OL,10,Fduty of candour.
OL,12,FSpeaking at a press conference in
OL,13,FDowning Street on Monday, the Prime
OL,14,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer said it was
OL,15,Fimportant to "get the balance right".
OL,17,FHe told reporters: "I care hugely that
OL,18,Fwe get this right, that we right the
OL,19,Fwrongs for very many families who have
OL,20,Fbeen let down and ensure a better
OL,21,Ffuture for families.
