OL,7,F"In relation to the duty of candour,
OL,8,Fwe've been clear that that matters.
OL,10,F"What we're now trying to do is just
OL,11,Fmake sure we get the balance right
OL,12,Fwhen it comes to the application of
OL,13,Fany principle to the security and
OL,14,Fintelligence agencies.
