OL,7,F"Obviously, I have to focus on the
OL,8,Fnational interest ` my primary duty as
OL,9,FPrime Minister, which is to keep this
OL,10,Fcountry safe and secure, that is the
OL,11,Fduty I hold above all other duties,
OL,12,Fand I take it really seriously, which
OL,13,Fis why we're just taking time to make
OL,14,Fsure that we get that balance
OL,15,Fabsolutely right."
