OL,3,CStarmer vows to 'get the balance
OL,4,Cright' after Hillsborough Law
OL,5,Camendment pulled
OL,7,FAn amendment tabled on Wednesday
OL,8,Fbrought spies within the scope of the
OL,9,Flegislation, after a number of
OL,10,Fcampaigners and politicians voiced
OL,11,Fconcerns that intelligence agencies
OL,12,Fwould be exempt from the law.
OL,14,FThe new amendment would have seen
OL,15,Fspies subject to the law subject to
OL,16,Fthe approval of the head of their
OL,17,Fservice, but campaigners said this
OL,18,Fwould give those running the security
OL,19,Fservices too much power over whether
OL,20,Fthey disclosed information.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
