OL,3,CStarmer vows to 'get the balance
OL,4,Cright' after Hillsborough Law
OL,5,Camendment pulled
OL,7,FMinisters are now speaking to
OL,8,Fcampaigners and bereaved families to
OL,9,Ftry to agree on how to move forward.
OL,11,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,12,FBurnham says he believes it should
OL,13,Fonly take "a matter of days" to decide
OL,14,Fthe next steps to introduce the law.
OL,16,FMr Burnham said the amendment "wasn't
OL,17,Fin the spirit of the Hillsborough Law"
OL,18,Fbut dismissed fears that the pulled
OL,19,Fdebate could cause significant delays
OL,20,Fto the long-awaited bill.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
