OL,7,F"Nobody is in any doubt that national
OL,8,Fsecurity is crucial. We've seen
OL,9,Finstances of terrorism here in Greater
OL,10,FManchester, and so has the Liverpool
OL,11,FCity Region.
OL,13,F"It's about having an arrangement that
OL,14,Fallows the truth to be told at the
OL,15,Ffirst time of asking, and 'making sure
OL,16,Fthe learning happens as quickly as it
OL,17,Fshould, to then make the (security)
OL,18,Farrangements even stronger."
