OL,7,FThe mayor spoke at a memorial event
OL,8,Ffor Olivia Campbell-Hardy, a victim of
OL,9,Fthe 2017 Manchester Arena Bombing.
OL,11,FMr Burnham went on: "I don't think
OL,12,Fthis will take weeks, hopefully just a
OL,13,Fmatter of days to come to a compromise
OL,14,Farrangement that protects the
OL,15,Fintegrity of the bill and the spirit
OL,16,Fof the Hillsborough law.
