OL,7,F"If we can get there quickly,
OL,8,Fhopefully the bill can be back in
OL,9,Fparliament in a week or so and then go
OL,10,Fto the Lords. In the end this will
OL,11,Fmake the bill stronger."
OL,13,FCampaign group Hillsborough Law Now
OL,14,Fsaid it welcomed the Government
OL,15,F"listening to the campaign, families,
OL,16,FMPs and supporters by withdrawing
OL,17,Ftheir security services amendment".
OL,19,FThe amendment put forward drew
OL,20,Fcriticism from campaigners and Labour
OL,21,Ffigures.
