OL,7,FLiverpool West Derby MP Ian Byrne had
OL,8,Fsaid he would not be able to support
OL,9,Fthe legislation with the Government's
OL,10,Famendments included.
OL,12,FLiverpool City Region mayor Steve
OL,13,FRotheram and Greater Manchester mayor
OL,14,FAndy Burnham said on Saturday that the
OL,15,FGovernment amendment "risks
OL,16,Fundermining the spirit of the
OL,17,Flegislation" and "creates too broad an
OL,18,Fopt-out" for the security services.
